namic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/146282/', '', 'Guar gum', 'Tinidazole, Tetracycline, Secnidazole, Cefixime, Amikacin, Tetracycline, Ganciclovir, Rifamycin, Kanamycin, Oxytetracycline, Netilmicin, More', 1767369485);
